---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Exhaust Research is an AI-powered product research platform that gives you honest, comprehensive product comparisons.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8">About Exhaust Research</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-surface-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg">
        Product research sucks. You Google something, get 10 SEO-optimized listicles that all
        recommend the same Amazon bestsellers, and walk away knowing less than when you started.
      </p>

      <p>
        Exhaust Research was built to fix that. When you ask a question here, we don't just
        check one source — we scrape Reddit discussions, review sites, manufacturer specs,
        forums, and more. Then we feed everything to AI and get a brutally honest analysis.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">What makes this different</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold mt-0.5">1.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Real sources.</strong> We pull from actual user discussions and reviews, not just manufacturer claims.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold mt-0.5">2.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">No sponsored picks.</strong> We don't get paid to recommend products. Affiliate links exist, but they don't influence rankings.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold mt-0.5">3.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Honest cons.</strong> Every product has drawbacks. We tell you what they are instead of burying them.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold mt-0.5">4.</span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Shareable results.</strong> Every research report gets a permanent link you can bookmark or share.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Who built this</h2>

      <p>
        I'm Chris — 20+ years in IT, Army veteran, homelab enthusiast. I got tired of doing
        the same manual research dance every time I needed to buy tech gear. So I built this
        tool for myself, then figured everyone else might want it too.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you're into IT, networking, or homelabs, check out the
        <a href="/blog" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors">blog</a>
        where I write about the stuff I actually use and build.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Transparency</h2>

      <p>
        This site uses Amazon Associates affiliate links. When you buy a product through one of our
        links, we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps keep the site running.
        Affiliate relationships never influence our product rankings or recommendations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
